  "scenes": [
    {
      "scene_index": 1,
      "label": "第一场",
      "characters_present": [
        "陆贾"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、陆贾同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为国忠良不到头，\n未央宫中一命休。\n人头高挂五凤楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官，陆贾。只因韩信在未央宫中言道：悔不听蒯彻之言，致有今日之祸。萧\n何奏道：韩信造反，乃是蒯彻主谋。因此汉王命我捉拿蒯彻。\n来，开道。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、陆贾同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 3,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮摇板"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "化子乙",
        "化子甲",
        "挣来江山旁人坐",
        "蒯彻",
        "陆贾"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "似这等装疯魔谁人猜破，\n不由我暗地里大笑呵呵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卑人，蒯彻，字文通。当年曾为韩信幕宾。那韩元帅在九里山前登台拜帅，后\n封三齐王之位。我也曾对他言道：留得霸王，三齐王位在；若是霸王死，三齐\n王即休。又言道：相君之面，不过封侯，相君之背，是贵不可言。那韩元帅不\n听我言，果然命丧未央宫。萧何奏道：韩信造反，乃是我蒯彻主谋。汉王差人\n捉拿于我，因此假装疯魔，以脱此案。思想忠良，好不伤感人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叹韩信大英雄无有结果，\n谁叫他不听劝自入网罗。\n相君面为人臣，相君背贵不可说。\n霸王死三齐王也不能活。\n因此上蒯文通假装疯魔。\n高堂母结发妻哪里顾得。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（化子甲、化子乙同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲、化子乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同数板） 不愁穿，不愁吃，每日长街讨饭食。不怕官，不怕吏，无牵无挂无忧虑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，今日天气晴和，你我行动行动，必有三分财气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲、化子乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哟，这有一疯魔汉，咱们来逗逗他。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（化子甲、化子乙同逗蒯彻。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "原来是我的儿——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻指化子乙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿子的哥哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻指化子甲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说哥哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯彻 （三笑） 哈哈，哈哈，啊，哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲、化子乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说疯汉，什么事情这么高兴啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今日里我和你们大家快乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，你听见没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听见什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说与我们大家快乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我们问问他。\n什么事大家快乐？说说我们听听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "洞房中燃花烛得配姣娥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，得配姣娥，你懂不憧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这得配姣娥，就是把鹅烧焦了，就叫得配娇娥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得了，得配姣娥，是娶老婆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们问问他的老丈人是谁。\n咳！疯汉，你的丈人是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我丈人就是那萧何丞相，"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，听见没有？他丈人是萧何丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好大来头。\n疯汉，你丈母娘是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "丈母娘就是那萧何的老婆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多新鲜哪。丈人是萧何，丈母娘不是萧何老婆，难道说是别人老婆？"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别招说了。\n疯汉，谁与你做的媒？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "秦始皇为媒证婚姻定妥，"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，他的媒人是秦始皇。\n那么你的媳妇是谁哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的妻好似那月里嫦娥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，月里嫦娥你见过没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "月里嫦娥，就是一只鹅飞到月亮里去了，就叫月里嫦娥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡说！月里嫦娥是长的好看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "疯汉，可有人与你贺喜？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "满朝中文武臣都来把喜贺，"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你给他们什么吃呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "无非是珍馐美味、海参鱼翅、还有那熊掌燕窝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，你听见没有？熊掌燕窝，你吃过没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "熊掌我可没有吃过，燕窝我倒吃过。就是人家屋檐下燕子搭的那个窝，拿下来\n用水煎煮，吃到肚里……"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那不牙碜吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就吃这个牙碜劲儿吗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡说。\n疯汉，可有人给你送亲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "送亲的大舅子是你们两个，"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，我们两个人成了大舅子了。\n疯汉，当你的大舅子有什么好处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "当我的大舅子有你们的酒喝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "饭都吃不上呢，还有酒喝哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说着说着肚中饿，\n用手取岀面馍馍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "化子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计，那旁有一伙人来了。咱们快走罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（化子甲、化子乙同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "耳旁边又听见金锣声过，\n怕的是平地里又起风波。\n也免得见了面大费唇舌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、陆贾同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将身儿且把那十字街过，\n且听那疯魔汉讲些什么。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩元帅呀！韩将军！哎！将军哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "盖世英雄无结果，\n未央宫中起风波。\n汗马功劳一场空，太不值得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，韩元帅呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "挣来江山旁人坐、陆贾",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "耳听得哭韩信想是蒯彻，\n蒯先生请出来我有话说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陆贾在此"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯彻来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那陆贾人忠正我不必藏躲，\n走向前施一礼把话来说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯先生装的好像啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "萧何逼我装疯，不得不如此。敢问大人，前来莫非拿我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉王听信萧何之言，命我捉拿先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好哇！我正要到金殿面见汉王，替韩信辩明冤屈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生若去，恐怕凶多吉少，不如逃走天涯，乃为上策。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大丈夫生而何欢，死而何惧。是非自有公论。快将刑具戴上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生乃当今名士，不必戴了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "入关约法三章，岂有不遵法度之理。你们戴、戴、戴呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "明知道是刀山决不藏躲，\n此一番见汉王我哪顾得死活。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、蒯彻、陆贾同下。）"
        }
      ],
