    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "一旦间听谗言韩侯命丧",
        "三齐王威权大兵多将广",
        "两旁边俱都是开国良将",
        "仗众卿灭项羽烟尘扫荡",
        "刘邦",
        "去掉了枷合锁油鼎来闯",
        "四值殿",
        "大太监",
        "天下的有心人纷纷言讲",
        "怒冲冲且把金殿上",
        "挽卿手同见过萧何丞相",
        "樊哙",
        "此一番替韩信辩明冤枉",
        "王陵",
        "站立在殿角下用目视望",
        "老萧何居然是左班丞相",
        "萧何",
        "蒯彻",
        "那王陵是孝子谁不钦仰",
        "陆贾",
        "陈平"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四值殿、四太监、大太监、王陵、樊哙、陈平、萧何、刘邦同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朕设朝龙耳听金钟三响，\n自三皇至炎帝多少帝王。\n商纣王宠妲己惑乱朝纲。\n周武王来伐纣社稷久长。\n在骊山焚烟墩自讨灭亡。\n逞干戈尚游说俱怀不良。\n五霸强七雄盛乱动刀枪。\n传二世朕与项接战咸阳。\n恨韩信谋大位倚势癫狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陆贾上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿住了蒯文通金殿来上，\n龙书案把此事启奏高皇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯彻拿到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，文通拿住了。将油鼎设在殿下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四值殿",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四值殿同抬油鼎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陆卿，替孤传旨，将反逆文通押上殿来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将反逆文通押上殿来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陆贾下。蒯彻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听得金銮殿把旨来降，\n来了我蒯文通为国忠良。\n上边厢坐定了大耳刘邦。\n有陈平出奇计站立一旁。\n鸿门宴小樊哙曾保高皇。\n单单的不见了擎天玉柱架海紫金梁。\n正所谓狡兔死、走狗烹、飞鸟尽、良弓藏、为国忠良无下场。\n站立在丹墀下志气昂扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "站立在殿角下用目视望、老萧何居然是左班丞相、那王陵是孝子谁不钦仰、两旁边俱都是开国良将、此一番替韩信辩明冤枉、怒冲冲且把金殿上、刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下站何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧何",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他就是反逆的文通。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错，他就是害人的萧何！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见孤为何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此地无有韩元帅，叫我跪哪一个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂不知韩信是孤之臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是桀犬吠尧，各为其主。我只知有韩元帅，不知有陛下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这等说来，无怪韩信图谋不轨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩信谋反不谋反，叛逆不叛逆，与我什么相干？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩信在未央宫言道：若听蒯彻之言，免遭此害！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带他上来质对。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩信被孤斩首了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这样看来，你就是无道的昏君！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见孤王无道？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你想啊，韩信造反，萧何奏道：蒯彻主谋。你就该将韩信下在监牢，遣人拿我\n前来，金殿之上，三头对案，情真，死而无怨。尽听一派谗言，杀了韩信！可\n怜哪，可怜！他十大汗马功劳，化为灰烬。天下有心人闻之，无不酸鼻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩元帅大功劳你不加赏，\n一旦间听谗言斩首未央。\n哪一个不骂你无道昏王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天下的有心人纷纷言讲、刘邦",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都道你舌辩徒果不虚谎，\n快将他下油鼎禁止癫狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何发笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不笑别人，笑的是汉王你。想当初覇王迁都于彭城，彭生谏道：大王若迁都\n中原，大势去矣。那霸王不听彭生之言，反将彭生油鼎烹之。今日汉王偏学那\n有勇无谋的项羽，烹我这有功无罪的蒯彻。岂不可笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难道你贪生怕死不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我非贪生，亦非怕死。只是我死之后，天下志士灰心，功臣丧胆。只恐你新来\n的江山，一旦休矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曾记得九里山登台拜将，\n设下了十面埋伏逼死霸王。\n韩信死汉江山也不久长。\n落一个烹油鼎万古名扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "一旦间听谗言韩侯命丧、去掉了枷合锁油鼎来闯、刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢。我来问你，韩信谋反可是真情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉王，你也不必问那韩信是忠是奸。但看那韩信在九里山登台拜将的时节，执\n掌兵权，将令一岀，山摇地动，若要自立，易如反掌。那时节他不谋反，怎么\n天下大定，兵权已销，他倒谋反？韩信又非痴人，陛下详参。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯文通说出了韩信冤枉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "油鼎抬下去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朕心中自思量大失主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗐，他这才明白了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领蒯彻即穿戴一品官蟒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯先生走罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝房冠带。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "换冠带做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做官。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今的官还做得么？我做怕了。不做了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难道你违抗圣命？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，这——"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要拿捏了。走罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大太监拉蒯彻同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朕想起秦无道国乱民荒。\n汉江山归统一国富民强。\n错疑他起反意夺孤家邦，故斩忠良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仗众卿灭项羽烟尘扫荡、三齐王威权大兵多将广、陈平",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丞相你不该把本奏上，\n险些儿又屈斩一个忠良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧何",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想当初都怨我一时莽撞，\n这也是我年迈奏本荒唐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王陵、樊哙",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从今后且莫要把本乱上，\n怕的是忠良臣俱无下场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧何",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在金殿一个个纷纷言讲，\n当万岁被他等羞辱一场。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说汉王全仗着舌辩高强。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯彻冒犯尊颜，死罪呀，死罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家忠义之言，寡人如梦初醒。朕发饷银与韩元帅，命彭越、英布等建造忠义\n贤庙，春秋两祭。封卿为舌辩侯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣不愿封侯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却是为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝中有萧何丞相一人足矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉江山仗众卿全力执掌，\n一殿臣休要论你弱我强。\n从今后俱同心共保家邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "挽卿手同见过萧何丞相、蒯彻",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "向前来施一礼尊声丞相，\n适才间乃是我蒯彻癫狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧何",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯先生休得要把礼谦让，\n乃是我把本章错奏大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众卿，光禄寺大摆筵宴，与舌辩侯贺喜压惊。退班。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四值殿、四太监、大太监、刘邦同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王陵、樊哙、陈平、萧何、蒯彻",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请驾回宫。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王陵、樊哙、陈平同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧何",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯先生装的好疯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丞相，你奏的好本哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯彻 （同笑） 哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧何、蒯彻同下。）"
        }
